description:
This is our second race on Vechs' Direct Fire race for the wool map. It was an absolutely fun, crazy, chaotic, intense, exciting, frustrating, rage inducing race!

The goal is to collect all 3 different wools and place them on your victory monument before the other team. These wool are very difficult to get. You are not allowed to use dyes on wool, and you are not allowed to enter the void area between the 2 lanes.

Vechs' Super Hostile maps thread: http://www.minecraftforum.net/topic/191908-ctmcollection-%E2%98%A0-vechs-supe...
